title: Squash Clinic
brief_description: Jahangir Khan - world squash champion and his coach Rahmat Khan feature in this comprehensive instructional video on squash technique. The player standard at which the video is aimed commences with beginners, includes the intermediate level and finishes with advanced instruction.
